s that could be created), but for sounds it seems like they should all be essentially the same. People can only really make so many different sounds, so it would be interesting to see if there is some reason why certain civilizations/language groups pick specific sounds while others do not. %0a>>%3c%3c%0a#foxend 210207-025044-436190#%0a%0a%0a%0a(:Section: :)%0a(:Category: PracticeCategory:)
